data.description: A very cozy home with several new updates has a lot of possibilities ! Finished Basement. Newer Windows. Mitigation systems in the basement. This is a 3 bedroom ranch style home in Tecumseh School District. It has a fenced in back yard and attached one car garage. This home has a eat in kitchen dining room. There is a two story shed in the back  yard it is a 12x14 with electric ran to it. All the appliances remain with the sale. This is one that wont last long on the market.
